        "Description": "Good evening, Agent AJ.\r\rYour assignment takes you to Paris, where a prestigious fashion event is drawing celebrities, designers, and powerful investors from across the world. Behind the scenes several individuals are using this event for criminal dealings.\r\rFive targets have been identified among the attendees. Tonight presents the perfect opportunity to remove them all in a single operation.\r\rHappy Birthday Agent. Good luck out there.",
